  "detailed_description": "<strong>ARMORED HEAD</strong> is a miniature shooter, where all the action takes place in one arena. The main character is a gladiator who fights against his opponents in pursuit of the grand prize. His task is to defeat <strong>30</strong> waves of opponents, unravel all the secrets of the arena, and win <strong>the gold cup</strong>. The character will be collecting gold coins, which will help him unlock some useful features of the arena, and become the winner in the battles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/805590/extras/54c526d65e08a601f7cbf60e14933ac0.poster.avif?t=1732463299\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/805590/extras/54c526d65e08a601f7cbf60e14933ac0.webm?t=1732463299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/805590/extras/54c526d65e08a601f7cbf60e14933ac0.mp4?t=1732463299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
